review_blob: Bottle. Strong cherry aroma, red color with easy red head. Taste is light sweetness, medium sourness. light body, thin feel, medium sour finish.

On tap at na 7.schode, Zilina. Fruity aroma. Amber to brown colour, clear liquid, rocky, white, creamy head. Medium sweetness, taste plums and easy alcohol. Full body, creamy texture, medium duration sweet finish.
On tap at na 7.schode, Zilina. Floral, herbs hops. Golden color, clear liquid, white head. Medium bitterness, light body, oily texture, flat carbonation with long bitter finish. Good beer for summer.

Bottle. Fruity, spicy and malty aroma. Golden color, hazy liquid with good strong creamy white head. Light sweetness, medium bitterness. Medium body, creamy texture, average carbonation and bitter finish.
On tap at na 7.schode, Zilina. Fruity aroma of oranges. mandarins and citrus hops. Golden color, cloudy liquid with creamy white head. Medium body, thick texture, flat carbonation and bitter finish.

Bottle. Golden to amber colour with white head. Aroma of bread malt, caramel and herbs hops, . Taste light to medium bitter and lightly sweet. Medium body with sticky texture, soft carbonation with easy honey and caramel finish.
Bottle. Orange, grapefruit, floral aroma. Orange to gold color with rocky white head. Taste is orange, grapfruit, strong bitter. Medium body with fizzy carbonation. Bitter finish
Bottle. White creamy head, floral and citrus hops aroma, golden color, clear liquid. Beginning is medium bitter with light body, thin texture, average carbonation and light bitter finish.
On tap at Pieansk pivovar, Pietany. Amber color, creamy head with creamy texture and medium body. Light bitter, bread and caramel malt.

Bottle shared w. wiedrzensky. Pleasant aroma of caramel and smoked malt. Reddish brown to dark brown color with white minimal head. Medium bitter taste with caramel. Medium body with lightly creamy texture and bitter finish.

Bottle. Shared w. wiedrzensky. Aroma nicely citrus. Nice golden color with white head but the minimum. Beginning with a pleasant hop taste citrus. Light body with thin texture and enough fizzy. Good and fresh light beer suitable for hot summer days.
beer_name: BrewDog Prototype Session India Pale Lager (IPL)

review_blob: Bottle. Aroma is malty, caramel. Appearance is good, amber-red colour and creamy head. Taste is roasted malt. Body light, texture creamy
